<li class="li1"><div class="de1"><span class="kw2">chown</span> s4vitar:s4vitar <span class="sy0">/</span>root<span class="sy0">/</span>.local <span class="re5">-R</span></div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1">&nbsp;</div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1"><span class="nu0">25</span>. Instalamos bat, lsd, fzf y ranger</div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1">&nbsp;</div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1"><span class="nu0">26</span>. Instalar el plugin <span class="kw2">sudo</span></div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1">&nbsp;</div></li>
<li class="li1"><div class="de1"><span class="nu0">27</span>. Instalamos nvim con el theme nord</div></li>
